| 红墙建筑 + 学生笑脸 | 结尾定格，品牌记忆 | "在这里，遇见未来。" |\n\n**总时长计算**：5+4+5+5+5+3+5+4+4+4+5+5 = **54秒** (加上转场和留白，目标控制在60秒左右)。\n\n## 3. 旁白策略\n*   **风格**：沉稳、深情、充满希望。\n*   **配音音色**：选用 "Ethan" (阳光、温暖、活力、朝气) 或 "Cherry" (亲切自然)。考虑到宣传片属性，选用 **Ethan** 更显大气。\n*   **分段**：严格按照上述时间轴，确保音画同步。\n\n---\n\n# 第二步：执行剪辑\n\n## 2.1 裁剪视频片段\n根据蓝图，优先使用 `cut_video` 精确裁剪指定时间段。\n\n', 'role': 'assistant', 'tool_calls': [{'type': 'function', 'id': 'chatcmpl-tool-9fb373b278fbfa1a', 'function': {'name': 'cut_video', 'arguments': '{"input_path": "/data1/liwenxi/agent/GenVideo/temp/selected_1_5zyEqn.mp4", "start_time": 0, "end_time": 5, "output_name": "clip_01_opening_aerial"}'}}, {'type': 'function', 'id': 'chatcmpl-tool-8ee3ae07dacf0536', 'function': {'name': 'cut_video', 'arguments': '{"input_path": "/data1/liwenxi/agent/GenVideo/temp/selected_5_11b7ta.mp4", "start_time": 0, "end_time": 4, "output_name": "clip_02_nature_lake"}'}}, {'type': 'function', 'id': 'chatcmpl-tool-85aa280430cd4e31', 'function': {'name': 'cut_video', 'arguments': '{"input_path": "/data1/liwenxi/agent/GenVideo/temp/selected_7_11X7gp.mp4", "start_time": 0, "end_time": 5, "output_name": "clip_03_gate_snow"}'}}, {'type': 'function', 'id': 'chatcmpl-tool-98aeaa57eac130e9', 'function': {'name': 'cut_video', 'arguments': '{"input_path": "/data1/liwenxi/agent/GenVideo/temp/selected_6_11171k.mp4", "start_time": 5, "end_time": 10, "output_name": "clip_04_stairs_hall"}'}}, {'type': 'function', 'id': 'chatcmpl-tool-81d99450892a005b', 'function': {'name': 'cut_video', 'arguments': '{"input_path": "/data1/liwenxi/agent/GenVideo/temp/selected_3_21M7ke.mp4", "start_time": 10, "end_time": 15, "output_name": "clip_05_library_reading"}'}}, {'type': 'function', 'id': 'chatcmpl-tool-8c6c6871b622b22c', 'function': {'name': 'cut_video', 'arguments': '{"input_path": "/data1/liwenxi/agent/GenVideo/temp/selected_4_y1d7e8.mp4", "start_time": 0, "end_time": 3, "output_name": "clip_06_library_detail"}'}}, {'type': 'function', 'id': 'chatcmpl-tool-b49b312d2619d60f', 'f